o 'Enlightenment' enquiry.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 7aSCIENCE / History.2bisacsh1 aHannan, Leonie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertManchester University Press 2023 eBook-Packagez9783111206455oZDB-23-MUP40uhttps://doi.org/10.7765/9781526153050zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781526153050zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781526153050/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-GOA  aZDB-23-MUPb2023